reviewText: Another good Jess Franco movie with his favorite actress Lina Romay.

There're many uncut scenes which is uncommon to find elsewhere, even those rated R(MPAA in the US), much less the country I came from. Thumbs up! But some scenes in the movie were not realistic; like the mirror from which the private eye took his photos. If he can see them making love, the couple can also see him vice versa. The one way glass is ok (more practical). Overall the movie is fine but the price is not fine, I intend to buy more like Roll Royce baby, Sexy sisters, some from the same director and producer but hesitating now.
